{
  "id": "adv_event_2308_01_03",
  "title": "パパと\n呼ばれし者",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ありえないよ。優に限って、パパ活なんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No way. There's no chance Yu would do something like a sugar daddy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.6147166252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "私だって、信じたくないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to believe it either‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8120184262,
      "endTime": 7.601995786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "優は思慮深い女の子だ\nそんな軽率なことをするとは、やっぱり考えられないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu is a thoughtful girl.\nI can't imagine her doing something so reckless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8120184262,
      "endTime": 13.9916556676,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……見ちゃったんです！\n優ちゃんが男の人とホテルに入って行くところを",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… we saw it!\nWe saw Yu-chan going into a hotel with a man.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1889574687,
      "endTime": 22.1784811656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "……あの、すみれ？　昨日も言ったけどパパって\n呼んでたしやっぱり本当のお父さんなんじゃ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ Sumire? Like I said yesterday‚ she called him \"Papa\".\nMaybe he really is her real father…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3889574687,
      "endTime": 29.924989001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "それは絶対ないよ！\n瑠依ちゃんだって二人の話を聞いてたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's definitely not true!\nRui-chan‚ you heard their conversation‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.122290802,
      "endTime": 35.475646972700005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "ええと……確か「パパ、上手だから」とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… she said something like \"Papa‚ you're so good\" and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.6889574687,
      "endTime": 41.021360937800004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、それ以上言わなくていい\n……見間違いじゃ、ないんだな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it‚ you don't need to say any more.\n…It wasn't a mistake‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.222290802,
      "endTime": 46.799479103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "私達が、優を見間違えるなんてありえません\n声も聞きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no way we could mistake Yu.\nWe even heard her voice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9967809041,
      "endTime": 51.7522228559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "し、しかし……優のお母さんは大女優で\nお父さんは大企業の経営者だったはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… Yu's mother is a famous actress and\nher father is a big company executive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9634475708,
      "endTime": 59.4712026595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "パパ活なんてする理由がない\n百歩譲って、年上の恋人という線は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She has no reason to be needed a sugar daddy.\nEven if we consider the possibility of an older boyfriend…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6685044606,
      "endTime": 66.35401442839999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "恋人のこと、「パパ」って呼ぶと思います？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you think she'd call a boyfriend \"Papa\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5513162295,
      "endTime": 70.5464863936,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……呼ばないよな、普通",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ normally she wouldn't.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7513162295,
      "endTime": 73.5821778456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、本当のお父さんじゃない……？\nそれに、恋人でもないんだとしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ if he's not her real father…\nand not her boyfriend either‚ then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7794796466,
      "endTime": 81.0357608318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……すみれの言う通りなのかもしれない\nあるいは厄介な事件に巻き込まれてる可能性も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Maybe Sumire is right.\nOr she might be involved in some troubling situation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2461463133,
      "endTime": 87.85061322840001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "優があの男の人に騙されてるってことですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you saying Yu is being tricked by that man!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9812539576,
      "endTime": 91.181254053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "三人でBIG4を目指そうって約束したのに\n……優、どうしちゃったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We promised to aim for the BIG4 together.\n…What's happening to Yu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5479180811,
      "endTime": 98.3536777971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんが騙されて傷つく姿なんて見たくないよ！\n{user}さん、私達どうすれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to see Yu-chan get hurt!\n{user}-san‚ what should we do…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5479180811,
      "endTime": 107.0749478815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……俺が確認してみる\nだから二人とも、思い詰めないでほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'll check it out.\nSo both of you‚ don't get too worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2812514144,
      "endTime": 112.2330882865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.4303900876,
      "endTime": 114.1637259641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、俺は信じてるよ\n優が君達を悲しませるようなことは、絶対しないって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I believe in Yu.\nShe would never do something to make you all sad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3970618405,
      "endTime": 121.0057466664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さんには\nいつも助けてもらってばかりですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ {user}-san.\nYou always help us so much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.7363812921,
      "endTime": 128.3831158159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……どうやって確認するんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "B-but… how will you check?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.5697146254,
      "endTime": 133.5321635085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "普通に聞いて、教えてくれるとは思えない\n尾行して証拠を押さえよう。話はそれからだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She wouldn't tell us if we asked normally.\nWe'll follow her and get evidence. We'll talk after that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7363812921,
      "endTime": 140.66139273619999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "なら私も連れて行って下さい。お願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then please take me with you. I'm begging you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8586945372,
      "endTime": 144.43547466569999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "私も行く！　じっと待ってるなんて出来ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll go too! I can't just sit and wait.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.6253612039,
      "endTime": 148.6067443368,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。でも危険なことはしないでくれよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Alright. But don't do anything dangerous‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.7920278706,
      "endTime": 152.9462001004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-night",
      "startTime": 154.8101675508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "うん。最近ちょっと寝不足やね\n夏フェスの準備もあって忙しいしなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Lately‚ I haven't been gettin' enough sleep.\nWith all the prep for the summer festival‚ I'm real busy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8768393037,
      "endTime": 163.3126897333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9166.687822400007
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-night",
      "startTime": 164.6435008841
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2308_01_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "……尾行、気付かれてませんね\n誰かと電話してるみたいですけど……",
      "translations": {
